tribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15329:\"<p><a href=\"http://wpcandy.com/?p=16870\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-16871\" title=\"Theme Madness Round 1 Day 2 voting\" src=\"http://wpcandy.com/files/2011/04/thememadnessround1day2-teaser.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p>This week we will be running through Round 1 of <a title=\"WPCandy Theme Madness 2011\" href=\"http://wpcandy.com/series-on/theme-madness-2011\">Theme Madness</a>, with eight games happening each day. Today’s games will be:</p><ul><li><a title=\"Graph Paper Press\" href=\"http://graphpaperpress.com/\">Graph Paper Press</a> vs. <a title=\"Panda Themes\" href=\"http://pandathemes.com/\">Panda Themes</a></li><li><a title=\"Theme Garden\" href=\"http://www.themegarden.com/\">Theme Garden</a> vs. <a title=\"BlogOhBlog\" href=\"http://www.blogohblog.com/\">BlogOhBlog</a></li><li><a title=\"ThemeJam\" href=\"http://themejam.com/\">ThemeJam</a> vs. <a title=\"Startbox\" href=\"http://wpstartbox.com/\">Startbox</a></li><li><a title=\"Organic Themes\" href=\"http://www.organicthemes.com/\">Organic Themes</a> vs. <a title=\"Storefront Themes\" href=\"http://storefrontthemes.com/\">Storefront Themes</a></li><li><a title=\"Theme Hybrid\" href=\"http://themehybrid.com/\">Theme Hybrid</a> vs. <a title=\"Xtreme Theme\" href=\"http://xtreme-theme.com/\">Xtreme Theme</a></li><li><a title=\"Pro Theme Design\" href=\"http://prothemedesign.com/\">Pro Theme Design</a> vs. <a title=\"Themes Kingdom\" href=\"http://www.themeskingdom.com/en/page/home/23\">Themes Kingdom</a></li><li><a title=\"Solostream\" href=\"http://www.solostream.com/\">Solostream</a> vs. <a title=\"ThemeShift\" href=\"http://themeshift.com/\">ThemeShift</a></li><li><a title=\"Crowd Favorite\" href=\"http://crowdfavorite.com/\">Crowd Favorite</a> vs. <a title=\"Working Wireframes\" href=\"http://workingwire