ges include a DVD of edited, high-resolution JPEG images, ready to print with unlimited printing rights. Each DVD has a special folder of 50-100 filtered images that are designed to highlight the style of your wedding. For instance, if the style of your wedding is urban elegance, filtered images may include speciality black and white effects along with sepia and vintage toned pictures. You have the option of choosing 15 additional images that you would like to have altered with special filters, at no extra cost. Each wedding package also includes a 2 hour engagement or After The Day session.  If an engagement session is not needed, an extra hour of wedding coverage can be added to your wedding day. Wedding albums are A La Carte and can be purchased with your package or if you prefer, after the wedding. Packages also include travel within 35 miles of Chicago limits.\r\n\r\nPlease inquire about pricing on my <a href=\"http://dawnephoto.com/contact/\"><strong>Contact</strong></a> page if you would like me to customize a package for you.  Also, please send me information about your wedding on my <a href=\"http://dawnephoto.com/contact/\"><strong>Contact</strong></a> page, I would love to hear from you!\r\n<h2>Albums</h2>\r\nAlbum pricing varies with size, cover options, pages and images with an average range of $700-$1000 for a full wedding album. Smaller parent books and companion books are also available for $300-$500. All books are custom-made and designed using your favorite images and design layout preferences. Album manufacturers include Finao, Leather Craftsmen, and Vision Art Books.\r\n<h2>Engagement Sessions</h2>\r\nEngagement sessions along with Day After sessions are available for more casual portraiture as an addition to your wedding prints.  Engagement sessions without a wedding package start at $400 for 2 hours of shooting time, unlimited locations and wardrobe changes.  If wedding packages are purchased, an Engagement Session of After The Day session is automatically included with most packages.  Engagement Sessions are always recommended, but if you decide to forego an engagement session, a credit will be added to your wedding package including an additional hour of wedding coverage or album credit.\r\n\r\n<em>Prices are subject to change without notice. One-third of your total price is required to guarantee your date and package price.</em>','pricing','','inherit','open','open','','22-revision-40','','','2011-03-21 10:43:46','2011-03-21 17:43:46','',22,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2011/03/21/22-revision-40/',0,'revision','',0),(607,1,'2011-01-12 21:32:30','2011-01-13 04:32:30','<div id=\"contact-form\" class=\"grid_7\">[contact-form 1 \"Contact form 1\"]</div>\r\n<div id=\"contact-info\" class=\"grid_3 push_1\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"grid_3 push_1\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">\r\n</span></strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"grid_3 push_1\"><strong>Telephone:</strong>\r\n(773) 334.0413</div>\r\n<div class=\"grid_3 push_1\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"grid_3 push_1\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"grid_3 push_1\"><strong>E-mail:</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"grid_3 push_1\"><a href=\"mailto:dawn@dawnephoto.com\" target=\"_blank\">dawn@dawnephoto.com</a></div>\r\n<div id=\"contact-info\" class=\"grid_3 push_1\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/dawnephotofans\"><img src=\"http://dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/facebook.png\" alt=\"facebook\" /></a><strong><a href=\"//twitter.com/Dawne007\"><img src=\"http://dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/twitter.png\" alt=\"facebook\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.weddingwire.com/reviews/dawn-roscoe-photography-chicago/aaf305bf573623a3.html \" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-528\" title=\"WeddingWire Icon\" src=\"http://dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/WeddingWire-Icon.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"25\" height=\"26\" /></a></strong>\r\n\r\n</div>','Contact','','inherit','open','open','','27-re