rague while traveling in Europe for one summer. After their first meeting, they spent one month trekking through Europe and decided to spend the rest of their lives together. Linus proposed to Maurine in Sweden (where he was born and raised) and they were engaged for one year and married this past July. Maurine’s details were a unique combination of whimsy chic with touches of purple and yellow to create a bright, modern palette. The cake was made to reflect the architectural silhouette of the Willis Tower in Chicago and in the color combination of her dress and decor details. The flowers and bridesmaid bouquets were also very sculptural and artful and created color accents to highlight her vintage bridal accessories.”\r\n\r\nTo see more images from this wedding, please link to my <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/dawnephotofans\"><em><span style=\"color: #5588aa;\">Facebook Fan Page</span></em></a><span style=\"color: #5588aa;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n[like]','Wedding Wire features Maurine and Linus’s wedding!','','inherit','open','open','','495-revision-36','','','2011-02-27 14:39:20','2011-02-27 21:39:20','',495,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2011/02/27/495-revision-36/',0,'revision','',0),(653,1,'2011-02-27 12:16:07','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Home Page','','draft','open','open','','','','','2011-02-27 12:16:07','2011-02-27 19:16:07','',0,'http://dawnephoto.com/?p=653',0,'post','',0),(652,1,'2011-02-27 10:13:45','2011-02-27 17:13:45','<h2>Wedding Packages</h2>\r\nAll wedding packages can be customized to suit your unique wedding day. Wedding coverage usually starts at 6 hours and can extend to 12 hours, if needed. All packages include a DVD of edited, high-resolution JPEG images, ready to print with unlimited printing rights.  Wedding albums are a la carte and can be purchased with your package or if you prefer, after the wedding. Packages also include travel to 30 miles outside of Chicago city limits. To give you more of an idea of pricing, below is a standard package for 2011:\r\n$3000 includes 8 hours of coverage and one 2nd photographer. You receive a DVD of your images sized at 8x12” with 300 dpi which means you can enlarge to 11x14” sizes.  All images are edited, color corrected, and have minor retouching applied. Also, I give you a Special folder of my favorite images (estimated 20-30) that have been retouched with special effects and filters. At no charge, I can apply filters up to 15 images of your choice.  Online proofing is also available for you on Pictage.com, along with print ordering for your friends and family. An Engagement session or After The Day session is also included in this package along with a $200 album credit if you do decide to order an album.\r\n\r\nPlease inquire about pricing on my <a href=\"http://dawnephoto.com/contact/\"><strong>Contact</strong></a> page if you need coverage for less or more time than the standard 8 hour package. I would be happy to customize a package  based on what you need for your special day. Also, please send me information about your wedding on my <a href=\"http://dawnephoto.com/contact/\"><strong>Contact</strong></a> page, I would love to hear from you!\r\n<h2>Albums</h2>\r\nAlbum pricing varies with size, cover option, pages and images with an average range of $700-$1000 for a full wedding album. Smaller parent books and companion books are also available for $300-$500.  All books are custom-made and designed using your favorite images and design layout preferences. Album manufacturers include Finao, Leather Craftsmen, and Vision Art Books.\r\n<h2>Engagement Sessions</h2>\r\nEngagement sessions along with Day After sessions are available for more casual portraiture as an addition to your wedding prints.  Engagement sessions start at $400 for 2 hours of shooting time, unlimited locations and wardrobe changes.  If wedding packages are purchased, an Engagement Session of After The Day session is automatically included with most packages.  Engagement Sessions are always recommended, but if you decide to forego an engagement session, a credit will be added to your wedding package including an additional hour of wedding coverage or album credit.\r\n<h2><em>Prices are subject to change without notice. One-third of your total price is required to guarantee your date and package price.</em></h2>','pricing','','inherit','open','open','','22-revision-36','','','2011-02-27 10:13:45','2011-02-27 17:13:45','',22,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2011/02/27/22-revision-36/',0,'revision','',0),(633,1,'2011-01-12 20:37:21','2011-01-13 03:37:21','[kml_flashembed publishmethod=\"static\" fversion=\"8.0.0\" movie=\"http://dawnephoto.com/wp-content/themes/roscoe-2010/SSP/the-celebration\" width=\"700\" height=\"560\" targetclass=\"flashmovie\" quality=\"high\" wmode=\"transparent\"]\r\n<p><a href=\"http://adobe.com/go/getflashplayer\"><img src=\"http://www.adobe.com/images/shared/download_buttons/get_flash_player.gif\" alt=\"Get Adobe Flash player\" /></a></p>\r\n[/kml_flashembed]','a beautiful day','','inherit','open','open','','14-revision-16','','','2011-01-12 20:37:21','2011-01-13 03:37:21','',14,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2011/01/12/14-revision-16/',0,'revision','',0),(634,1,'2011-01-23 23:00:47','2011-01-24 06:00:47','[kml_flashembed publishmethod=\"static\" fversion=\"8.0.0\" movie=\"http://dawnephoto.com/wp-content/themes/roscoe-2010/SSP/prewedding.swf\" width=\"700\" height=\"530\" targetclass=\"flashmovie\" quality=\"high\" wmode=\"transparent\"]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://adobe.com/go/getflashplayer\"><img src=\"http://www.adobe.com/images/shared/download_buttons/get_flash_player.gif\" alt=\"Get Adobe Flash player\" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/kml_flashembed]','pre-wedding sessions','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision-17','','','2011-01-23 23:00:47','2011-01-24 06:00:47','',6,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2011/01/23/6-revision-17/',0,'revision','',0),(635,1,'2011-01-12 20:37:59','2011-01-13 03:37:59','[kml_flashembed publishmethod=\"static\" fversion=\"8.0.0\" 