25','<a href=\"http://dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/Real-Chicago-Weddings-3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-570\" title=\"Real-Chicago-Weddings-3\" src=\"http://dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/Real-Chicago-Weddings-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"615\" height=\"2269\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>From the Photographer: </em></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><em> </em></strong>“What makes this wedding special: Maurine met Linus at a nightclub in Prague while traveling in Europe for one summer. After their first meeting, they spent one month trekking through Europe and decided to spend the rest of their lives together. Linus proposed to Maurine in Sweden (where he was born and raised) and they were engaged for one year and married this past July. Maurine’s details were a unique combination of whimsy chic with touches of purple and yellow to create a bright, modern palette. The cake was made to reflect the architectural silhouette of the Willis Tower in Chicago and in the color combination of her dress and decor details. The flowers and bridesmaid bouquets were also very sculptural and artful and created color accents to highlight her vintage bridal accessories.”\r\n\r\nTo see more images from this wedding, please link to my <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/dawnephotofans\"><em><span style=\"color: #5588aa;\">Facebook Fan Page</span></em></a><span style=\"color: #5588aa;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n[like]','Wedding Wire features Maurine and Linus’s wedding!','','inherit','open','open','','495-revision-34','','','2011-02-12 12:27:25','2011-02-12 19:27:25','',495,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2011/02/12/495-revision-34/',0,'revision','',0),(672,1,'2011-02-27 14:55:59','2011-02-27 21:55:59','','press','','inherit','open','open','','655-revision-7','','','2011-02-27 14:55:59','2011-02-27 21:55:59','',655,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2011/02/27/655-revision-7/',0,'revision','',0),(673,1,'2011-04-07 07:52:33','2011-04-07 14:52:33','this is where press will go....','pr