le, and quintessential moments. With my photography influences and background, my goal is provide all of my clients with modern and timeless images, with some artistic, spontaneous fun!','about me','','publish','closed','closed','','about','','','2011-03-02 10:20:47','2011-03-02 17:20:47','',0,'http://dawnephoto.com/',0,'page','',0),(266,1,'2010-08-28 12:08:22','2010-08-28 19:08:22','','About','','inherit','closed','open','','265-revision','','','2010-08-28 12:08:22','2010-08-28 19:08:22','',265,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2010/08/28/265-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(267,1,'2010-08-28 12:09:31','2010-08-28 19:09:31','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras eget vulputate enim. Pellentesque ullamcorper sem vel felis rhoncus feugiat. Phasellus dictum luctus varius. Morbi quis ipsum et nulla hendrerit pellentesque. Duis fringilla odio in mauris varius hendrerit. Aenean ut augue quam. Duis lobortis, quam gravida elementum lacinia, ligula sem sagittis nisl, at ultricies elit felis eu lorem. Praesent imperdiet, lectus a semper viverra, sapien erat ullamcorper lacus, eu sollicitudin nulla enim quis metus. Suspendisse nec tellus sem. Cras diam mi, sollicitudin in semper eu, accumsan nec lorem. Phasellus dolor eros, faucibus ac luctus auctor, vestibulum nec nisl. In vitae purus eros. Nullam vel est lorem.','About','','inherit','closed','open','','265-revision-2','','','2010-08-28 12:09:31','2010-08-28 19:09:31','',265,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2010/08/28/265-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(269,1,'2010-08-28 12:11:10','2010-08-28 19:11:10','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras eget vulputate enim. Pellentesque ullamcorper sem vel felis rhoncus feugiat. Phasellus dictum luctus varius. Morbi quis ipsum et nulla hendrerit pellentesque. Duis fringilla odio in mauris varius hendrerit. Aenean ut augue quam. Duis lobortis, quam gravida elementum lacinia, ligula sem sagittis nisl, at ultricies elit felis eu lorem. Praesent imperdiet,