-27 10:00:28','2011-02-27 17:00:28','','FileItem-5908-casestudy','','inherit','open','open','','fileitem-5908-casestudy','','','2011-02-27 10:00:28','2011-02-27 17:00:28','',0,'http://dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/FileItem-5908-casestudy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(846,1,'2011-03-31 14:46:56','2011-03-31 21:46:56','Ashlyn and Matt are both architects who met in graduate school at the University of Michigan. Both love Chicago architecture and wanted their engagement session to be chock full of skylines, buildings and texture. We first ventured to North Beach where the snow was melting from the February blizzard and temperatures were warm enough for a great engagement session. Afterwards, we went along the Dearborn bridge in the Loop and ended on LaSalle Street. Ashlyn and Matt were so comfortable throughout the entire day, which made for some great candid moments. Congratulations to the couple and I can\'t wait for your wedding in early July!!\n\n<a href=\"http://www.dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_1705dyno.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-840\" title=\"IMG_1705dyno\" src=\"http://www.dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_1705dyno.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_8857ginger.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-841\" title=\"IMG_8857ginger\" src=\"http://www.dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_8857ginger.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_8889fsbw.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-842\" title=\"IMG_8889fsbw\" src=\"http://www.dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_8889fsbw.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_8923fairy.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-843\" title=\"IMG_8923fairy\" src=\"http://www.dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_8923fairy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_9088ray.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-844\" title=\"IMG_9088ray\" src=\"http://www.dawnephoto.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_9088ray.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /></a>','Ashlyn and Matt Chicago engagement!','','inherit','open','open','','839-revision','','','2011-03-31 14:46:56','2011-03-31 21:46:56','',839,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2011/03/31/839-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(651,1,'2011-02-19 09:56:55','2011-02-19 16:56:55','<h2>Wedding Packages</h2>\r\nAll wedding packages can be customized to suit your unique wedding day. Wedding coverage usually starts at 6 hours and can extend to 12 hours, if needed. All packages include a DVD of edited, high-resolution JPEG images, ready to print with unlimited printing rights.  Wedding albums are a la carte and can be purchased with your package or if you prefer, after the wedding. Packages also include travel to 30 miles outside of Chicago city limits. To give you more of an idea of pricing, below is a standard package for 2011:\r\n$3000 includes 8 hours of coverage and one 2nd photographer. You receive a DVD of your images sized at 8x12” with 300 dpi which means you can enlarge to 11x14” sizes.  All images are edited, color corrected, and have minor retouching applied. Also, I give you a Special folder of my favorite images (estimated 20-30) that have been retouched with special effects and filters. At no charge, I can apply filters up to 15 images of your choice.  Online proofing is also available for you on Pictage.com, along with print ordering for your friends and family. An Engagement session or After The Day session is also included in this package along with a $200 album credit if you do decide to order an album.\r\n\r\nPlease inquire about pricing on my <a href=\"http://dawnephoto.com/contact/\"><strong>Contact</strong></a> page if you need coverage for less or more time than the standard 8 hour package. I would be happy to customize a package  based on what you need for your special day. Also, please send me information about your wedding on my <a href=\"http://dawnephoto.com/contact/\"><strong>Contact</strong></a> page, I would love to hear from you!\r\n<h2>Albums</h2>\r\nAlbum pricing varies with size, cover option, pages and images with an average range of $700-$1000 for a full wedding album. Smaller parent books and companion books are also available for $300-$500.  All books are custom-made and designed using your favorite images and design layout preferences. Album manufacturers include Finao, Leather Craftsmen, and Vision Art Books.\r\n<h2>Engagement Sessions</h2>\r\nEngagement sessions along with Day After sessions are available for more casual portraiture as an addition to your wedding prints.  Engagement sessions start at $400 for 2 hours of shooting time, unlimited locations and wardrobe changes.  If wedding packages are purchased, an Engagement Session of After The Day session is automatically included with most packages.  Engagement Sessions are always recommended, but if you decide to forego an engagement session, a credit will be added to your wedding package including an additional hour of wedding coverage or album credit.\r\n\r\n<em>Prices are subject to change without notice. One-third of your total price is required to guarantee your date and package price.</em>','pricing','','inherit','open','open','','22-revision-35','','','2011-02-19 09:56:55','2011-02-19 16:56:55','',22,'http://dawnephoto.com/blog/2011/02/19/22-revision-35/',0,'revision','',0),(637,1,'2011-02-13 18:04:34','2011-02-14 01:04:34','[kml_flashembed publishmethod=\"static\" fversion=\"8.0.0\" movie=\"http://dawnephoto.com/wp-content/themes/roscoe-2010/SSP/aroundtown.swf\" width=\"750\" height=\"530\" targetclass=\"flashmovie\" quality=\"high\" wmode=\"transparent\"]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http